            innerBlocks: [],
            innerHTML:
              '\u003cp>How can professionals recharge and emotionally recover from their experience of working through the challenges of 2020-21? May is\u003ca href="https://www.mhanational.org/mental-health-month"> Mental Health Awareness Month\u003c/a>; make a real commitment to yourself. Your mental health is precious. Consider these tips as you contemplate your emotional recovery.\u003c/p>\n',
