            blockName: "core/paragraph",
            attrs: [],
            innerBlocks: [],
            innerHTML:
              '\u003cp>\u003ca href="https://www.cdc.gov/physicalactivity/walking/index.htm">Routine movement reduces stress and anxiety\u003c/a>, according to the CDC. Incorporate routines that you can manage: morning\u003ca href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L4Z7lix6Qao"> sun salutations\u003c/a>, lunchtime walks, or evening bike rides. Pick your practice and commit.\u003c/p>\n',
